the lights, which is
something that you're not

00:31:40.130 --> 00:31:41.730
going to have to worry about.

00:31:41.730 --> 00:31:43.470
The lighting
actually-- I mean, it's

00:31:43.470 --> 00:31:45.770
by far the most time
consuming thing.

00:31:45.770 --> 00:31:47.740
But it gives you
an idea of-- that's

00:31:47.740 --> 00:31:49.740
a really great point I'm
glad that you made it--

00:31:49.740 --> 00:31:51.198
that it's more than
just the amount

00:31:51.198 --> 00:31:53.840
of time it takes for
you to say a line.

00:31:53.840 --> 00:31:55.490
Hopefully you won't
have that panic,

00:31:55.490 --> 00:31:57.880
because the way this
class is structured,

00:31:57.880 --> 00:31:58.870
it's very front heavy.

00:31:58.870 --> 00:32:00.390
We've had a lot
of lectures so far

00:32:00.390 --> 00:32:02.990
but after the editing
