actually the very last one.

00:32:04.520 --> 00:32:08.180
And the rest of the
class period will mostly

00:32:08.180 --> 00:32:11.620
be for you to work on
stuff during class time.

00:32:11.620 --> 00:32:13.570
So don't worry too
much about that.

00:32:13.570 --> 00:32:15.760
We tried to anticipate
that for you guys.

00:32:15.760 --> 00:32:18.370
But just to let you know.

00:32:18.370 --> 00:32:22.160
I forgot had a couple examples
for you for some of the stuff

00:32:22.160 --> 00:32:23.430
that Chris was mentioning.

00:32:23.430 --> 00:32:25.250
And I'll play them real quick.

00:32:25.250 --> 00:32:28.277
MALE IN VIDEO: What is the most
awesome place in the world?

00:32:28.277 --> 00:32:30.610
Seems like that would be
